title: For Sale/Trade:  Union fire arms 16 ga double barrel Toledo,O
postcontent: Local made shotgun. Very scarce. Very well made! The Union Fire Arms company was located in Toledo Ohio and manufactured fine shotguns from 1903 to 1917. In 1917, Ithaca absorbed the company. If you are from the Toledo area and want an amazing conversation piece this one is for you.According to Gun Digest, a Union double barrel is worth between $300 in poor, non functional condition to $1400 in excellent condition. Also, there is a 15-20% premium for single trigger models, which this has. Based on my opinion only, I would say that it appears to me as if this gun would fire and function as desired if attempted. This is certainly a very seldom seen amazing piece of local history. It belongs on the wall of a local collector.

postcontent: For sale, German WWII k98 rifle with leather sling, dot 1944 with matched bolt and barreled action, including rear sight, there are no import markings on this rifle. Also included, what looks like either a very late War or early Post War leather sling. postcontent: Not perfect, as it is 70 year old military refurbished firearm, but you will not be disappointed as I paid the extra $$$ for hand select for cosmetic appearance and bore condition when I purchased this great rifle.  The M44 was produced between 1944 and 1949, and is a shorted/lighter version of its predecessor, the Russian Mosin Nagant 91/30.  Bolt action rifle holds 5 rounds of 7.62x54r ammo.  Would say 99% of the cosmoline has been removed from this rifle (fortunately), but would clean the bore before firing.  This M-44 comes with the bayonet that can be side folded for convenience.  Re-arsenaled/refurbished by Molot in Russia (don't see them listed as a Manufacturer)???  Still in the box I received it in, with pamphlet printed in english, small vintage oil can, and basic tool kit for dis-assembly/assembly.  No expert, but the numbers I can see all match. Gun has a date of 1944.  These are getting harder to find with the import ban due to the conflict Russia is in.  Must have valid Kansas Driver's License for identification.
